\section{Workflow Design}

The workflow will be designed as a modular Snakemake pipeline consisting of independent analysis stages connected through explicitly defined input and output files. This design improves readability, reproducibility, scalability, and maintainability.

Optional workflow switches will allow users to skip selected quality control or pre-processing steps if such analyses were already performed. In addition, the workflow will support partial execution of individual analysis stages. For example, the quality control module may be executed independently prior to running the complete workflow, enabling intermediate inspection of sequencing quality before downstream analyses are performed.

