\section{Expected Workflow Outputs}

The workflow produces the following deliverables:

\begin{enumerate}
    \item assembled viral genomes in FASTA format,
    \item phylogenetic trees in Newick format,
    \item graphical tree visualizations in PDF or PNG format,
    \item text files containing average sequence variability values for sliding windows,
    \item variability plots across genomic coordinates,
    \item MultiQC reports summarizing quality control results.
\end{enumerate}

These outputs provide complementary information regarding genome reconstruction quality, evolutionary relationships, and genomic variability.

